### Options
- `abs <x> <y>` — absolute position (bypass auto layout).
- `alt <image>` — highlight image, scaled to original.
- `hflip` / `vflip` — flip horizontally/vertically.
- `text <text> <xoff> <yoff>` — overlay static text.
- `cvartext <cvar> <xoff> <yoff>` — overlay text from cvar.
- `scale <value>` — scale both dimensions.
- `transient` — reupload when gamma/brightness changes.
- `setimage <cvar>` — image name from cvar.

